snippet.title: Gemini 3 Gives You Superpowers: Here’s How to Unlock Them
snippet.description:
In this video, I cover how Google has finally caught up with OpenAI by launching two groundbreaking AI models, Gemini 3 and Nano Banana.  These models excel in creating advanced viual outputs, multi-modal understand, both things that make them an invaluable tool for content creators, entrepreneurs, and marketers.

If you enjoyed this video, the best way to support the continuation of more videos is by liking, sharing and subscribing to my channel.  

I really appreciate the support and I'll see you for the next one!

Have an app idea but don't know where to begin or have limited time? 

I highly recommend trying out Vibecode App.  Me and my cofounders have been working hard on this tool for most of 2025 and we want to enable 1M people to build software without writing a single line of code.

Try building your first mobile app completely for free here: https://vibecode.go.link/fNyxn
 ➡️use promo code GOOGLE to get your first app build for free!
